⛏️ 1. DATA MINES (INGESTION LAYER)

These are sources of signal, not scraped illegally, but:

Types of mines

1. First-party mines (strongest)
	•	your apps (Pokemon ranking, taste engines, etc.)
	•	embedded SDK in partner apps
	•	surveys disguised as interactions (pairwise > forms)

2. Federated mines (high leverage)
	•	partners keep raw data
	•	you receive aggregated gradients / embeddings
	•	no raw personal data leaves source

3. Synthetic mines (bootstrapping)
	•	simulated users
	•	controlled experiments
	•	A/B tradeoff environments

⸻

Output of mines

All mines emit the same unit:

Comparison Event Stream

Everything becomes:

(U, A, B, choice, context, metadata, confidence, timestamp)

That standardization is your first moat.

