🧪 2. REFINERY (PROCESSING LAYER)

This is where raw “ore” becomes usable signal.

Stage A: Cleaning

Remove:
	•	bots
	•	spam taps
	•	low-effort noise
	•	duplicated sessions

Score events by quality:
	•	dwell time
	•	consistency
	•	follow-through
	•	contradiction rate

⸻

Stage B: Normalization

Convert everything into unified meaning:

Raw action	Normalized signal
swipe right	weak positive
super like	strong positive
pause + reject	conflicted negative
choose A over B	pairwise positive
revisit item	delayed positive
purchase	confirmed preference


