⚠️ CRITICAL GUARDRAILS (NOT OPTIONAL)

If you skip these, the whole thing dies.

1. Consent-based ingestion

Users or partners explicitly allow data use.

2. Privacy-preserving computation
	•	federated learning
	•	differential privacy
	•	aggregation thresholds

3. No deanonymization

You don’t need identity to extract value.

4. Separation of layers
	•	raw data never leaves source
	•	only signals/embeddings flow outward

5. Transparency hooks

Partners know what’s being extracted and why.

